aws::graph::propositions: Boeing-Stearman Model 75 Military Operators
The Republic of China Air Force (ROCAF) used Boeing-Stearman Model 75 aircraft until 1958.
Colombian Air Force operated Boeing-Stearman Model 75 aircraft.
